title: Pinocchio in Outer Space [1965]
description:
Pinocchio in Outer Space (1965)


Its blast off time for Pinocchio!
So that he can become a real boy again instead of just wooden puppet Pinocchio
decides to do a really good deed.
With his new friend nurtle the turtle, the jet propelled turtle, he zooms off into 
space to capture Astro the flying whale wwhich is terrorising space craft thoughout
the galaxies.
See Pinocchio as never before - weightless as an astronaut!
Battling with giant space creatures! Trapped in a martian earthquake!

So fasten your seatbelts and get set for take-off to a fantastic astral
world full of wonders beyond all imagination.
